    <div class="content-entry">
        <h2 class="title sub-title text-upper">LET’S START GROWING YOUR BUSINESS</h2>
        <div class="row">

            <div class="content-block">
                <div class="large-4 large-push-8 columns">
                    <div class="img-block customPointerBusiness"><img src="http://angedove.com/wp-content/themes/angedove-theme/img/logo-market.png" alt="" onclick="location.href='http://marketmybusinessforme.com/';"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="large-8 large-pull-4 columns">
                    <p>You set up your business because you had something great to offer the world. But you’re not a marketing expert and you don’t have the time nor focus nor possibly knowledge to draw up a viable marketing plan. And even if you do, you don’t have the team inhouse to create the marketing materials you need: email direct mailers, blog posts, social media posts, social media ads, etc.</p>
                    <p>It’s frustrating that you can’t get your message out there and at how costly it is to outsource at MNC prices. I hear you, because I used to be in the same boat. That’s why I’ve created special marketing packages aimed specifically at your size business.</p>
                    <a href="http://marketmybusinessforme.com/" class="button button-wide customBusiness"><span>TAKE A LOOK AT OUR PACKAGES</span></a>
                </div>
            </div> <!--content-block--->
            <div class="content-block">
                <div class="large-4 large-push-8 columns">
                    <div class="img-block customPointerBusiness"><img src="http://angedove.com/wp-content/themes/angedove-theme/img/logo-brand.png" alt="" onclick="location.href='http://proofperfect.com.sg/branding.html';"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="large-8 large-pull-4 columns">
                    <p>When you started your business, chances are you took the creation of your marketing materials step by step. You probably had them done by different design agencies along the way. Trouble is, you realise now that you don’t have a brand – just a mismatch of different looks across different marketing pieces. And branding goes beyond just a uniform look. Your brand should communicate your values and everyone in your company should understand and live by your brand to create a consistent experience for your clients.</p>
                   
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" data-open="form-modal" aria-controls="form-modal" id="3yosun-reveal" aria-haspopup="true" tabindex="0" class="button button-wide customBusiness"><span>ASK ABOUT MY FREE BRAND CONSULTATION</span></a>
                </div>
            </div> <!--content-block--->
            <div class="content-block">
                <div class="large-4 large-push-8 columns">
                    <div class="img-block customPointerBusiness"><img src="http://angedove.com/wp-content/themes/angedove-theme/img/logo-create.png" alt="" onclick="location.href='http://proofperfect.com.sg/editorial.html';"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="large-8 large-pull-4 columns">
                    <p>You can’t ignore the online world. Like it or not, that is where most of your clients hang out these days. And the numbers are only set to increase as the millennials get spending power. Not being online is costing you in incalculable missed lead opportunities.</p>
                    <p>And in the online world content is king, both words and images. To fill your lead pipeline, you need to be posting regular blog posts and social media updates as well as sending emails to your list. But as a small business owner, who has the time. I never used to make time for my business and it nearly cost me my business. It has to be a priority. The good news is you don’t have to do it yourself. My crack team of copywriters, editors and designers are here to create the content for you – content that your target audience will want to read and that will raise your brand and online presence. Clients will start seeking you out instead of the other way around.</p>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" data-open="form-modal" aria-controls="form-modal" id="3yosun-reveal" aria-haspopup="true" tabindex="0" class="button button-wide customBusiness"><span>BOOK A MEETING WITH ME TO FIND OUT MORE. </span></a>
                </div>
            </div> <!--content-block--->
        </div>
    </div> <!--content-entry--->
